<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CorpusVisuals</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root {
    --primary: #FC8B01;
    --bg: #000000;
    --card: #0f0f0f;
    --text: #ffffff;
}

* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
}

header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 60px;
    background: black;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #111;
}

header img {
    height: 40px;
}

nav a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-left: 30px;
    font-weight: 500;
}

nav a:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
}

.hero {
    height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 52px;
    max-width: 800px;
    line-height: 1.2;
}

.hero span {
    color: var(--primary);
}

section {
    padding: 100px 60px;
}

h2 {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-size: 32px;
}

.services {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
}

.card {
    background: var(--card);
    padding: 30px;
    border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
}

.card h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.portfolio {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 15px;
}

.portfolio img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 220px;
    object-fit: cover;
}

.about {
    max-width: 800px;
}

.contact input,
.contact textarea {
    width: 100%;
    background: #050505;
    border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding: 12px;
    margin-top: 15px;
    color: white;
}

button {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: black;
    border: none;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    margin-top: 15px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px;
    border-top: 1px solid #111;
    font-size: 14px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<img src="logo.png" alt="CorpusVisuals Logo">
<nav>
<a href="#services">Leistungen</a>
<a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
<a href="#about">Über mich</a>
<a href="#contact">Kontakt</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<h1>
Visuelle Inhalte für <span>Unternehmen</span>, Events und Marken.
</h1>
</section>

<section id="services">
<h2>Leistungen</h2>

<div class="services">
<div class="card">
<h3>Eventfotografie</h3>
<p>Dokumentation von Firmenveranstaltungen, Konferenzen und Messen in professioneller Qualität.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Videoproduktion</h3>
<p>Imagefilme, Eventvideos und Social-Media-Content für moderne Unternehmenskommunikation.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Unternehmensfotografie</h3>
<p>Authentische Bilder für Websites, Marketing und Recruiting.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="portfolio">
<h2>Portfolio</h2>

<div class="portfolio">
<img src="p1.jpg">
<img src="p2.jpg">
<img src="p3.jpg">
<img src="p4.jpg">
</div>

</section>

<section id="about">
<h2>Über CorpusVisuals</h2>

<p class="about">
CorpusVisuals steht für moderne und hochwertige Foto- und Videoproduktion.
Ich unterstütze Unternehmen dabei, ihre Events, Marken und Teams visuell professionell zu präsentieren.
</p>

</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">
<h2>Kontakt</h2>

<input type="text" placeholder="Name">
<input type="email" placeholder="E-Mail">
<textarea rows="5" placeholder="Nachricht"></textarea>
<button>Anfrage senden</button>

</section>

<footer>
© 2026 CorpusVisuals
</footer>

</body>
</html>
